{"tid":1908610,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國洗錢集團規模逾百億 菲律賓下令調查","createTime":"2020-03-03T11:40:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T11:59:41.000Z","uid":75656,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c32a38ba827cda8382d5e9e4a98eb439cf6fdf3f","tid":1908610,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:40:27.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕菲律賓藍帶委員會主席參議員戈登（Richard Gordon）數天前警告，中國國民湧入菲國並夾帶「過量金錢」，呼籲當局進行調查，而週一菲國財政部公告，政府已開始調查中國公民的洗錢案，目前掌握2集團洗錢共3.68億美元（約新台幣110.3億元）。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》報導，此2集團被稱為「羅德里奎」（Rodriguez）和「中國人」（Chinese），已被菲國海關總署追蹤，自去年6月開始各自攜帶2億美元和1.68億美元入境（約新台幣59.9億與50.35億元）。財政部稱，犯案人透過每週2到3次旅行、每次12000披索至50000披索（約新台幣7091至29548元）飛往菲律賓，接頭的軍警則讓他們略過檢查。<br />\n<br />\n旅客最多可攜帶1萬美元或其他等值外幣進出菲律賓。戈登表示，從去年12月至今年2月，中國以帶來約1.8億美元現金。而上個月反對派參議員Risa Hontiveros便透露，有些移民官員讓沒有身份證的中國公民入境，讓他們得以在線上賭場非法工作，這也促使菲國總統杜特蒂（Rodrigo Duterte）下令翻新移民系統。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐馬尼拉大使館去年8月則表示，大量與賭博有關的資金正非法流出中國，往菲律賓流入，這些資金建立的賭博行業正雇用大量中國籍員工、擠壓菲律賓的線上賭場業，而菲國線上賭場業的目標客群正是中國賭徒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3087125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3087125&d=HqwfJ7ndl2RLmQbQQ2LVpvrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=b8e80695\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3087125&h=2ea033ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3087125</a>"},{"pid":"71effe30ad88edd4dc8f930e582d0f4f11e555ce","tid":1908610,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:51:13.000Z","msg":"洗得果百幾億就唔好學人叫洗黑錢集團啦 <br />\n香港一個師奶喺屋企單獨都洗到成70億黑錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/china/2013/03/130312_hk_woman_money_laundering.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchina%2F2013%2F03%2F130312_hk_woman_money_laundering.shtml&d=HqwfJ7ndl2RLmQbQQ2LVpvrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=6f4c9899\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchina%2F2013%2F03%2F130312_hk_woman_money_laundering.shtml&h=53945a18\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/china/2013/03/130312_hk_woman_money_laundering.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"2e00122a7a14d25e83c21a7823d98ab71a89285f","tid":1908610,"uid":293012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:52:56.000Z","msg":"咪又係比班賓賓貪左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f8e610c8826e0e5534003ba1f1e10d60e82ecf","tid":1908610,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:59:41.000Z","msg":"三億就算啦"}]}